  "text": "The d 3 -differentials in the Atiyah-Hirzebruch spectral sequence for twisted K-theory were identified by Atiyah and Segal in [CITATION_1] as the difference between Sq 3 and the twisting. In the same paper the higher differentials are determined in terms of Massey products. One may ask if also the higher differentials in the slice spectral sequence can be described in terms of Massey products.",
